languages.text: "Я спрошу с вас позже, что это было и как вы это допустили. Но пока — вернемся к неотложному".
"I will enquire of you what that was and how you let it happen later. For now, however, let us return to the matter at hand."
languages.original_text: "Я спрошу с вас позже, что это было и как вы это допустили. Но пока — вернемся к неотложному".

traits.locale_text: "I shall ask you later what that was and how you managed to let it happen. But let us return to the urgent matter at hand for now."

languages.text: “等这件事情结束之后，我得问问你那到底是什么东西，是怎么出现的。不过现在，我们还是先办完眼下的要紧事吧。”
languages.original_text: "I will enquire of you what that was and how you let it happen later. For now, however, let us return to the matter at hand."

traits.locale_text: “等这件事情结束之后，我会问你那究竟是什么东西，以及它是怎么出现的。不过，我们还是先办完眼下的要紧事吧。”
traits.speaker: Inquisitor

languages.text: "Ich werde Euch später dazu befragen, was das war und wie Ihr es zulassen konntet. Für Erste wenden wir uns aber wieder dringlicheren Themen zu."
languages.original_text: "I will enquire of you what that was and how you let it happen later. For now, however, let us return to the matter at hand."

traits.locale_text: "Ich frage Euch später, was das war und wie Ihr es zugelassen habt. Aber vorerst müssen wir uns um die dringlichere Angelegenheit kümmern."
traits.speaker: Inquisitor

languages.text: 「それが何なのか、どうしてそうなったのかは後ほど尋ねるとしよう。だが今は、目の前の問題に戻るとしよう」
languages.original_text: "I will enquire of you what that was and how you let it happen later. For now, however, let us return to the matter at hand."

languages.text: "Onun ne olduğunu ve nasıl ortaya çıkmasına izin verdiğini daha sonra soracağım. Şimdilik elimizdeki meselelere dönelim."
